text: Ali Ebrahimbeigi (, born 19 May 1984) is an Iranian futsal player. He is currently a member of Omid Pirouz Kavir Aran o Bidgol. == Honours == === Club === * Iranian Futsal Super League ** Runners-up (1): 2008–09 (Eram Kish Qom) * Iranian Futsal Hazfi Cup ** Champion (1): 2013–14 (Mahan Tandis Qom) * Iran Futsal's 1st Division ** Runners-up (1): 2016–17 (Atoliyeh Tehran Qom) == References == Category:1984 births Category:Living people Category:People from Qom Category:Iranian men's futsal players Category:Almas Shahr Qom FSC players Category:Dabiri FSC players Category:Sohan Mohammad Sima FSC players
